        <abstract>
            <p>Wishes to propose John Lubbock as a member of the Entomological Society.</p> 
<p>Asks for B. H. Hodgson’s pamphlet on sheep ["Tame sheep and goats", <hi rend="italic">J. Asiat. Soc. Bengal</hi> 16 (1847): 1003–26]. Asks for odd numbers of GRW’s work [<hi rend="italic">A natural history of the Mammalia</hi> (1846–8)]. Regrets that this work has stopped.</p> 
        </abstract>
